		<div id="post_message_385675">Flying mounts would be a fun AA.<br />
<br />
I dont want a carpet(those are more for erudites maybe =) ) but a pegasus or griffin sounds cool. In D&amp;D you have the mount spell where the mounts capabilities increase as your lvl increase. Maybe it could be based on how much total AA you have. 50aa normal mount, 100aa it can walk on water, 150aa it can fly. 200aa better speed? <br />
<br />
Maybe a shadowmount(transparant horse) with flaming hoves for wizards rar  <img src="images/smilies/grinyes.gif" border="0" alt="" title="Grin Yes" class="inlineimg" /></div>
